  MODULE .......: NNFRIEX.p
  TASK .........: creates an Excel File of Calls TO 020-numbers
  APPLICATION ..: NN
  AUTHOR .......: PT
  CREATED ......: 14.01.1998
  CHANGED ......: 11.09.2002 jp / some fix
  Version ......: M15
